All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AvoidObstacle
    The AvoidObstacle helps the robot to avoid the obstacle using ultrasonic and wall follower.
    ExtractRobot
    This class extracts your robot into a separate wbo file to make it easier to manage the competition.
    FileLoader
    Loads a playing field layout into resources from a file.
    LightLocalizer
    The light localizer.
    Main
    Main class of the program.
    Movement
    Movement class covers the robot the robot movement and rotation.
    Navigation
    The Navigation class is used to make the robot navigate around the playing field.
    Odometer
    The odometer class keeps track of the robot's (x, y, theta) position.
    Overpass
    Line segment representing the overpass.
    Point
    Represents a coordinate point on the playing field grid.
    Region
    Represents a region on the playing field grid, delimited by its lower-left and upper-right corners (inclusive).
    Resources
    Class for static resources (things that stay the same throughout the entire program execution), like constants and hardware.
    T03Controller
    Wrapper class for webots to start the main project method.
    UltrasonicLocalizer
    The ultrasonic localizer.
